{"tid":1657833,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被問是否「攬炒之母」　林鄭月娥稱形容目無法紀破壞者","createTime":"2019-10-16T09:15:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T09:23:54.000Z","uid":104865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f2e80753b50b50851984be7305526902553a04b0","tid":1657833,"uid":104865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:15:17.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥在記者會被問到，是否「攬炒之母」時回應說，目無法紀去破壞香港的人，更適合有關形容。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，見到暴徒破壞香港，打爛設施，看不到他們期望爭取甚麼，唯一感覺只是他們想香港衰落。她強調自己沒有相關心態，仍希望以最大決心，繼續服務香港，指願意聆聽、互動，不要將自己想法過早加諸於社會，將香港帶出困局，強調是對香港的承諾。<br />\n<br />\n她說未來日子將會難，又說今早進入立法會都演變成激烈惡劣的情況，相信未來要面對有關場面的機會不少，但仍希望能共建香港。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n她表示，見到暴徒破壞香港，打爛設施，看不到他們期望爭取甚麼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />平行時空？？？？？<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486552-20191016.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486552-20191016.htm&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVllsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=1ae6a0fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486552-20191016.htm&h=9481be13\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486552-20191016.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8ab887229a0d4a5c65bb3b63be6e1a18b3d3c0a5","tid":1657833,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:17:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zBif5mg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzBif5mg.jpg&h=44757529&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"002b6b888b3e08df5edffb48e5e4352e3049304f","tid":1657833,"uid":101552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":